OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDenmark tells some migrants
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto work for benefits       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some migrants in Denmark will now be   
OL,6, required to work 37 hours a week in    
OL,7, order to receive welfare benefits.     
OL,9,FIt will be a requirement for those who 
OL,10,Fhave been on benefits for three to four
OL,11,Fyears, and who have not reached a      
OL,12,Fcertain level of proficiency in Danish.
OL,14,FPrime Minister Mette Frederiksen said  
OL,15,Fthe rules were directly aimed at women 
OL,16,Ffrom "non-Western backgrounds" living  
OL,17,Fon benefits.                           
OL,19,FDenmark has repeatedly tightened its   
OL,20,Fimmigration policies in recent years.  
